 qemu-server (9.1.10) trixie; urgency=medium
 
   * fix #7383: agent: skip the 'guest-fsfreeze-freeze' QMP command when the
     guest filesystem is already frozen, to avoid the confusing 'the command is
     not allowed' error users would otherwise see.
 
   * snapshot: tpm state: fall back to the storage-layer snapshot type when the
     TPM drive is not handled by the QEMU Storage Daemon, since the drive is in
     that case not attached to any QMP-managed process.
 
